        "TileImage": "$($repository 0a6fce5e-4eec-4794-965a-1f29b340e550).Image",
        "Description": "Greetings 47.\rI know that you dont take contracts out of hate and spite and that the targets would have to have done something, that is why i picked out partners that are also partners in crime. horrible, awful crimes.\rDiana will fill you in on what they did.\rOther than that, i want to see couples dying, i got no one so i dont wanna see others in love.\r\rGood luck breaking hearts like you are breaking necks 47.",
